1) Login to tronlink wallet through browser extension
2) Move to setting -> node -> shasta network
3) Copy your account address
4) Open https://www.trongrid.io/shasta/#request 
5) Paste your address and click request button
6) Go back to your wallet, You will get test coins
7) Install tronbox (npm install -g tronbox)
8) Check if it is installed (type tronbox)
9) go to 3 lines below setting in tronlink and then export account, then copy private key
10) In tron project there is file named tronbox.js, add private key copied in front of key named private key
11) Compile contract ( tronbox compile --compile-all)
12) Migrate contract ( tronbox migrate --reset --network shasta)
13) yarn / npm install
14) yarn start/ npm start